OL,3,CBreakthrough could lead to 'big leaps'
OL,4,Cin battery performance, scientists say
OL,6,FScientists have announced a
OL,7,Fbreakthrough in our understanding of
OL,8,Fhow batteries work, saying it could
OL,9,Flead to "big leaps" in battery
OL,10,Fperformance in the future.
OL,12,FResearchers at Dundee and Warwick
OL,13,Funiversities say that for the first
OL,14,Ftime they have identified the key role
OL,15,Foxygen plays in storing and releasing
OL,16,Fa battery's energy.
OL,26,@qD@IOUqD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
