FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782733687
OL,3,CBreakthrough could lead to 'big leaps'
OL,4,Cin battery performance, scientists say
OL,6,FIt was previously thought that during
OL,7,Fthe charging process much of the
OL,8,Factivity happens in metal elements
OL,9,Finside the battery, such as nickel,
OL,10,Fcobalt, or iron, and that oxygen in
OL,11,Fthe battery was "passive".
OL,13,FHowever, the team said advanced
OL,14,Fcomputer modelling and laboratory
OL,15,Fexperiments have shown that oxygen
OL,16,Fplays a much more active role in the
OL,17,Fcharging and discharging process.
OL,26,@sD@QOUsD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
