OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782733687
OL,3,CBreakthrough could lead to 'big leaps'
OL,4,Cin battery performance, scientists say
OL,6,FThey said the findings could lead to
OL,7,Fthe development of batteries for
OL,8,Felectronics and vehicles that charge
OL,9,Ffaster, last longer, and are safer to
OL,10,Fuse.
OL,12,FDr Hrishit Banerjee, a theoretical
OL,13,Fphysicist at Dundee's faculty of
OL,14,Fscience, engineering and business,
OL,15,Fsaid: "Global populations have become
OL,16,Fincreasingly reliant on renewable
OL,17,Fenergy technologies and advanced
OL,18,Fenergy storage systems from everything
OL,19,Ffrom the mobile phones in our pockets
OL,20,Fto the cars we drive.
OL,26,@wD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782733687
OL,3,CBreakthrough could lead to 'big leaps'
OL,4,Cin battery performance, scientists say
OL,6,F"This has made understanding the
OL,7,Ftechnology underpinning electronic
OL,8,Fprocesses inside battery materials
OL,9,Fincreasingly important.
OL,11,F"This research is crucial and gives us
OL,12,Fa new understanding of how batteries
OL,13,Ffunction at a fundamental level."
OL,15,FThe study compared two of the main
OL,16,Flithium-ion battery cathodes used
OL,17,Ftoday ` phosphates and layered oxides.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782733687
OL,3,CBreakthrough could lead to 'big leaps'
OL,4,Cin battery performance, scientists say
OL,6,FTogether these forms of batteries are
OL,7,Fused for a host of applications,
OL,8,Fincluding electric vehicles and
OL,9,Fportable electronics such as mobile
OL,10,Fphones and laptops.
OL,12,FThe study found that while phosphates
OL,13,Fshowed little oxygen participation,
OL,14,Fthe layered oxides showed
OL,15,F"significant" electron extraction from
OL,16,Foxygen.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
