PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782733687
OL,3,CBreakthrough could lead to 'big leaps'
OL,4,Cin battery performance, scientists say
OL,6,FDr Banerjee said: "By improving our
OL,7,Fknowledge of what is occurring at a
OL,8,Ftiny, atomic level within batteries,
OL,9,Fwe can make big leaps in improving
OL,10,Ftheir performance in the real world.
OL,12,F"Current technologies are limited by
OL,13,Fthe understanding of the underlying
OL,14,Fphysics of how and why batteries fail
OL,15,Fover time.
OL,17,F"This general framework will help
OL,18,Fdesign batteries with much longer
OL,19,Flifetimes."
OL,26,@nD@SOUtD@AOUyD@AOU{D@KO]
